{"tid":1245460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：馮驊我屌你老母呀！","createTime":"2019-06-20T10:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T09:25:49.000Z","uid":215755,"like":97,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30acfe3a5c5f386a5424c996f297aa9a12e8b0b5","tid":1245460,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ajj4DH02Ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4ajj4DH02Ac&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=adb28d24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ajj4DH02Ac</a><br />\n<br />\n【睇片】選管會簡介會 梁天琦：馮驊，食屎喇你<br />\n2016/8/2 &mdash; 20:02<br />\n<br />\n選管會晚上7點在九龍灣國際展貿中心，為立法會候選人舉行簡介會，多名獲選管會通知已確認參選資格的候選人及其助選團陸續到場，將會為各候選人進行抽籤，決定其名單選舉編號。選舉管理委員會主席馮驊發言時，一度有泛民參選人走到台前叫口號，被裁定參選提名無效的本土民主前線梁天琦站在椅上高叫，「馮驊，食屎啦你！屌你老母！」<br />\n<br />\n職員隨即要求保持安靜，注意用辭。在場也有人以粗口辱罵馮驊。在場則有人大力拍掌叫喊以示支持梁天琦，梁其後離開會場，稱再聽下去已無意思。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊開始發言時，一批泛民參選人走到台前高叫「反對政治篩選，維護公平選舉」等口號，抗議選管會阻止部份參選人出選，一度令簡介會暫停。"},{"pid":"c954d62cf72d309b0ecfc03564d76d388f991e29","tid":1245460,"uid":9899,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"天琦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bac4d1d3170c22c88d3b60dbffc60fbe517bfa","tid":1245460,"uid":35221,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馮驊！我屌你老母呀！馮驊！屌你！"},{"pid":"ec8fa798bf2c444de61d2254722adafc52544805","tid":1245460,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2574c1cbac89e7b837b41560ce29edb192e3ad0","tid":1245460,"uid":45459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"天琦好波"},{"pid":"35aa42bc4c95f70f0fecf5affe98ac5bb1a69329","tid":1